Inspirational speaker Turia Pitt , who suffered horrific burns when she was caught in a bushfire , has revealed she still struggles to overcome her near-death ordeal .
The 27-year-old said just the smell from a barbecue brought back the traumatic moment she was trapped for four hours where she suffered burns to 65 per cent of her body .
Ms Pitt also revealed she ran her first marathon last month since the fire .